 and photodissociation are also taking place in Sgr B2\nin addition to more established phenomena such as widespread low--velocity\nshocks.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 5 Mar 2003 15:31:11 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-07"}
